betterquesting:10.desc:8:
You can feel the waves of hate radiating out of her eyes. Don't even think about getting close without an Apiarist Suit. Must be bred in the Nether. Breed them from Eldritch and Infernal.

[note]Breeder's Notes: Infernal bees are used to make both this species and spiteful, which is next in line from hateful. That means you'll probably start winding up with spitefuls while trying to make this species. Since this is a progression to more interesting species, you could say it doesn't matter, but:

1. Skipping straight to spiteful means not getting this quest done and then losing your progression.
2. Maybe you want to do a smoldering bee, which needs this one.

What we recommend is tucking away any spitefuls you get and just act like that didn't happen until you finish this bee. If the princess starts turning spiteful and you don't want to just start a new one, you'd want to pump it with infernal or eldritch (pick one!) until you've cleaned out the spiteful trait.[/note]
